      <title><![CDATA[Add sitemap]]></title>
      <url>http://yoursite.com/2016/09/12/hexo/add-sitemap/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr>
<h2 id="Add-SiteMap"><a href="#Add-SiteMap" class="headerlink" title="Add SiteMap"></a>Add SiteMap</h2><hr>
<p>Welcome to <a href="http://elizachen.cc/" target="_blank" rel="external">My Blog</a> !</p>
<p>Following are the steps:</p>
<h4 id="Install-plugin"><a href="#Install-plugin" class="headerlink" title="Install plugin"></a>Install plugin</h4><ul>
<li><p>Install hexo-generator-sitemap.</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-sitemap</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="Config-the-module"><a href="#Config-the-module" class="headerlink" title="Config the module."></a>Config the module.</h4><ul>
<li><p>_config.yml</p>
<p> #####Please don’t use following sentence, it will remove other plugins and most pages will be removed:</p>
<p>  <del>plugins:</del> <del>- hexo-generator-sitemap</del></p>
<p> <strong>DO NOT define plugins! Let Hexo search for them (recommend) or define ALL the plugins you used.</strong><br> Please refer <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues/1848" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues/1848</a> for more information.<br> Please use following:</p>
  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">sitemap:</div><div class="line">  path: sitemap.xml</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="Deploy-yours-codes"><a href="#Deploy-yours-codes" class="headerlink" title="Deploy yours codes."></a>Deploy yours codes.</h4><ul>
<li><p>Then You can find your sitemap.xml under your blog. Such as <a href="http://elizachen.cc/sitemap.xml" target="_blank" rel="external">http://elizachen.cc/sitemap.xml</a>.  </p>
<pre><code><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo g</div><div class="line">hexo d</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</code></pre></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="Commit-to-google-webmaster"><a href="#Commit-to-google-webmaster" class="headerlink" title="Commit to google webmaster."></a>Commit to google webmaster.</h4><ul>
<li>Press your site.<br><img src="/images/hexo_sitemap_1.png" alt="google webmaster 1"></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><p>Press sitemap block.</p>
<p><img src="/images/hexo_sitemap_2.png" alt="google webmaster 2"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Add your sitemap:<br><img src="/images/hexo_sitemap_3.png" alt="google webmaster 3"></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="Waiting-for-google-finish-verify"><a href="#Waiting-for-google-finish-verify" class="headerlink" title="Waiting for google finish verify."></a>Waiting for google finish verify.</h4><p>Thanks for reading.</p>
<p>My Blog Motto is <strong><em>I just write the articles which are useful! ^_^ </em></strong></p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
